{"timestamp": "2025-12-03 11:04:40.596509", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission recorded.\n\nSummary of submission:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- faulty_devices: host_1_1_1_1, host_2_1_1_1\n- root_cause_name: host_missing_ip\n\nRecommended next steps (brief):\n- On affected hosts: check DHCP client process/status and logs (dhclient/systemd-networkd/NetworkManager), run tcpdump on eth0 during DHCP renew to see DISCOVER/OFFER/REQUEST/ACK, and verify network namespaces.\n- If DHCP client not running or failing, restart/enable it; if running but not applying lease, investigate permissions/network scripts or race conditions.\n- Verify switch port mapping if needed and confirm MACs match DHCP lease records.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2318, "output_tokens": 150, "total_tokens": 2468, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1792}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
